title: insurance agency
extract: An insurance agency, sometimes called an insurance brokerage or independent agency, solicits, writes and binds policies through many different insurance companies. ... Agencies can decided which insurance carriers they would like to represent and which personal and business products they would like to offer.Apr 18, 2014
